7). Mucho mв”ңГӯs al fondo, el nuevo y descomunal edificio de la Facultad de Medicina y Ciencias, que se inaugurarв”ңГӯ un par de aв”ңв–’os despuв”ңВ®s. Y mв”ңГӯs allв”ңГӯ no hay mв”ңГӯs. Fuente visual: AHPZ, Estudio Coyne, c.1891", "year": 1891, "year_from": 1891, "year_to": 1891, "era": "Siglo XIX", "zone": "CASCO HISTв”ңГҙRICO", "lat": 41.655977, "lng": -0.879206, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/14984794535.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/thumbs/14984794535.webp", "source": "https://www.flickr.com/photos/zaragozaantigua/14984794535/", "author": "Zaragoza Antigua (Flickr)", "rights": "Uso educativo", "tags": []}, {"id": 23809, "title": "Plaza del Pilar 1930", "description": "\"Entrada principal al templo de Nuestra Seв”ңв–’ora del Pilar\". En la imagen, la \"Puerta Baja\", y aspecto parcial de la plaza del Pilar.", "year": 1930, "year_from": 1930, "year_to": 1930, "era": "Anos 30", "zone": "CASCO HISTв”ңГҙRICO", "lat": 41.656295, "lng": -0.87824, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/15421894968.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/thumbs/15421894968.webp", "source": "https://www.flickr.com/photos/zaragozaantigua/15421894968/", "author": "Zaragoza Antigua (Flickr)", "rights": "Uso educativo", "tags": []}, {"id": 24888, "title": "Pl. del Pilar 1949", "description": "AHPZ. Estudio Coyne. \"Obras del actual Ayuntamiento. Plaza de Nuestra Seв”ңв–’ora del Pilar. Remodelaciв”ңв”Ӯn de la fachada de la Catedral Basв”ңВЎlica de Nuestra Seв”ңв–’ora del Pilar\".", "year": 1949, "year_from": 1949, "year_to": 1949, "era": "Anos 40", "zone": "CASCO HISTв”ңГҙRICO", "lat": 41.65608, "lng": -0.877876, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/15021790335.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.